          <div id="description-5" class="problem-description">
            <div class="problem-description-text">
              <h6 class="fw-bold mt-3">Company Challenge:</h6>
              <p>
                Ensuring the safety and compliance of workers with essential
                personal protection equipment (PPE) on job sites, such as
                construction areas or electrical fields, is a critical
                challenge. The goal is to develop a system that effectively
                detects and monitors the usage of specific safety gear, such as
                hard hats, and ensures workplace safety protocols are being
                followed. The solution should address the following key
                objectives:
              </p>

              <h6 class="fw-bold">Key Features to Address:</h6>
              <h6 class="fw-bold">PPE Compliance Monitoring:</h6>
              <p>
                Develop a solution that uses advanced sensing technologies to
                monitor whether workers are wearing required safety gear (e.g.,
                hard hats) within designated work zones, ensuring compliance
                with safety regulations.
              </p>
              <h6 class="fw-bold">Real-Time Detection:</h6>
              <p>
                Implement real-time detection systems that instantly identify
                instances where workers may not be following PPE requirements,
                triggering immediate alerts for corrective action.
              </p>
              <h6 class="fw-bold">Customizable Parameters:</h6>
              <p>
                Allow safety officers or site managers to customize monitoring
                parameters based on the specific safety needs of each workplace,
                ensuring flexibility for different types of personal protection
                equipment (PPE) used across various industries.
              </p>
              <h6 class="fw-bold">Integration with Access Control:</h6>
              <p>
                Explore the possibility of integrating the PPE monitoring system
                with access control systems, ensuring that workers who are not
                wearing the necessary safety gear are restricted from entering
                high-risk or dangerous areas, creating a more proactive safety
                culture.
              </p>
              <h6 class="fw-bold">User-Friendly Interface:</h6>
              <p>
                Design an intuitive, user-friendly interface that allows site
                managers and safety officers to easily monitor and track PPE
                compliance, ensuring a quick and effective response to any
                safety breaches.
              </p>
              <h6 class="fw-bold">Considerations for Solution Design:</h6>
              <h6 class="fw-bold">Privacy Concerns:</h6>
              <p>
                Address privacy concerns by implementing measures to protect
                workers' personal data and identities, ensuring compliance with
                privacy regulations and ethical standards for data handling.
              </p>
              <h6 class="fw-bold">Scalability:</h6>
              <p>
                Design the system to be scalable, capable of supporting various
                workforce sizes and adapting to different work environments,
                from small sites to large-scale industrial operations.
              </p>

              <p>
                We challenge innovators to create a comprehensive solution that
                ensures PPE compliance, enhances safety protocols, and promotes
                a culture of proactive protection in high-risk work
                environments, while balancing privacy and scalability
                requirements.
              </p>
            </div>
            <button class="btn btn-secondary action-button">Continue</button>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item" id="problem-6">
          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
              <span class="problem-number">6</span>
              <span class="problem-title"
                >Sustainable Bottle Packaging Solution</span
              >
              <span>| Packaging / Logistics</span>
            </div>
            <button
              class="btn btn-primary btn-sm"
              onclick="toggleDescription(6)"
